-14T16:36:36Z","publishedAt":"2021-05-08T09:53:05Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-24T19:04:27Z","tagName":"306-3.0.6","isPrerelease":false,"releaseAssets":[{"name":"MiuiHome_3.0.6.apk","contentType":"application/vnd.android.package-archive","downloadUrl":"https://github.com/Xposed-Modules-Repo/com.yuk.miuihome/releases/download/306-3.0.6/MiuiHome_3.0.6.apk"}]},{"name":"3.0.3 Release","url":"https://github.com/Xposed-Modules-Repo/com.yuk.miuihome/releases/tag/303-3.0.3","description":"1. 修复深色模式bug\r\n2. 修复模块在设备重启后无法激活的问题","descriptionHTML":"<ol>\n<li>修复深色模式bug</li>\n<li>修复模块在设备重启后无法激活的问题</li>\n</ol>","createdAt":"2021-06-14T16:36:36Z","publishedAt":"2021-05-05T15:02:13Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-24T19:02:24Z","tagName":"303-3.0.3","isPrerelease":false,"releaseAssets":[{"name":"MiuiHome_v3.0.3.apk","contentType":"application/vnd.android.package-archive","downloadUrl":"https://github.com/Xposed-Modules-Repo/com.yuk.miuihome/releases/download/303-3.0.3/MiuiHome_v3.0.3.apk"}]},{"name":"3.0.0 Release","url":"https://github.com/Xposed-Modules-Repo/com.yuk.miuihome/releases/tag/300-3.0.0","description":"1. Fix version code\r\n2. Add App Icon","descriptionHTML":"<ol>\n<li>Fix version code</li>\n<li>Add App Icon</li>\n</ol>","createdAt":"2021-06-14T16:36:36Z","publishedAt":"2021-05-04T12:35:29Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-24T19:00:21Z","tagName":"300-3.0.0","isPrerelease":false,"releaseAssets":[{"name":"MiuiHome_v3.0.0.apk","contentType":"application/vnd.android.package-archive","downloadUrl":"https://github.com/Xposed-Modules-Repo/com.yuk.miuihome/releases/download/300-3.0.0/MiuiHome_v3.0.0.apk"}]},{"name":"1.0 First Release","url":"https://github.com/Xposed-Modules-Repo/com.yuk.miuihome/releases/tag/1-1.0","description":"MiuiHome v1.0\r\n实现了[原版](https://github.com/YuKongA/MiuiHome)的所有功能","descriptionHTML":"<p>MiuiHome v1.0<br>\n实现了<a href=\"https://github.com/YuKongA/MiuiHome\">原版</a>的所有功能</p>","createdAt":"2021-06-14T16:36:36Z","publishedAt":"2021-05-04T08:46:04Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-24T18:58:20Z","tagName":"1-1.0","isPrerelease":false,"releaseAssets":[{"name":"MiuiHome_v1.0.apk","contentType":"application/vnd.android.package-archive","downloadUrl":"https://github.com/Xposed-Modules-Repo/com.yuk.miuihome/releases/download/1-1.0/MiuiHome_v1.0.apk"}]}],"readme":"# MiuiHome\n\n__Hook for MIUI Launcher - Xposed__ [![Android CI](https://github.com/1767523953/MiuiHome/actions/workflows/main.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/1767523953/MiuiHome/actions/workflows/main.yml)\n\n### 如何使用\n__激活模块后重启一次系统桌面，再打开桌面设置，点击模块设置选项即可弹出弹窗.__\n\n__模块设置不在本应用界面!!请在MIUI桌面设置中打开Dialog来设置.__\n\n### 前世今生\n__原仓库：[YuKongA/MiuiHome](https://github.com/YuKongA/MiuiHome)__\n\n__新仓库：[1767523953/MiuiHome](https://github.com/1767523953/MiuiHome)__\n \n### 模块涉及内容\n\n- 平滑动画.\n- 文件夹模糊.\n- 动画速度调节.\n- 后台模糊级别.\n- 状态栏时钟常显.\n- 后台卡片大小调节.\n- 后台卡片圆角大小调节.\n- 下载时图标的水波纹特效.\n- 后台卡片图标文字间距调节.\n- 强制为高端设备(默认启用)等.\n\n### Credit\n[FC](https://github.com/ejiaogl/FuckCoolapk)\n[BiliRoaming](https://github.com/yujincheng08/BiliRoaming/blob/master/LICENSE)\n[XposedBridge](https://github.com/rovo89/XposedBridge)\n[LSPosed](https://github.com/LSPosed/LSPosed)\n[androidx.annotation](https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+/androidx-master-dev/annotation/annotation/)\n\n### 软件截图\n![Screenshot](https://github.com/1767523953/MiuiHome/blob/main/Screenshot/pc1.jpg)\n\n### License\n[AMTPL v1 + GPL-3.0](LICENSE)\n","readmeHTML":"<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-miuihome\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#miuihome\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>MiuiHome</h1>\n<p><strong>Hook for MIUI Launcher - Xposed</strong> <a href=\"https://github.com/1767523953/MiuiHome/actions/workflows/main.yml\"><img src=\"https://github.com/1767523953/MiuiHome/actions/workflows/main.yml/badge.svg\" alt=\"Android CI\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h3>\n<a id=\"user-content-如何使用\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>如何使用</h3>\n<p><strong>激活模块后重启一次系统桌面，再打开桌面设置，点击模块设置选项即可弹出弹窗.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>模块设置不在本应用界面!!请在MIUI桌面设置中打开Dialog来设置.</strong></p>\n<h3>\n<a id=\"user-content-前世今生\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%96%E4%BB%8A%E7%94%9F\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>前世今生</h3>\n<p><strong>原仓库：<a href=\"https://github.com/YuKongA/MiuiHome\">YuKongA/MiuiHome</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>新仓库：<a href=\"https://github.com/1767523953/MiuiHome\">1767523953/MiuiHome</a></strong></p>\n<h3>\n<a id=\"user-content-模块涉及内容\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>模块涉及内容</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>平滑动画.</li>\n<li>文件夹模糊.</li>\n<li>动画速度调节.</li>\n<li>后台模糊级别.</li>\n<li>状态栏时钟常显.</li>\n<li>后台卡片大小调节.</li>\n<li>后台卡片圆角大小调节.</li>\n<li>下载时图标的水波纹特效.</li>\n<li>后台卡片图标文字间距调节.</li>\n<li>强制为高端设备(默认启用)等.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>\n<a id=\"user-content-credit\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#credit\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Credit</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/ejiaogl/FuckCoolapk\">FC</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/yujincheng08/BiliRoaming/blob/master/LICENSE\">BiliRoaming</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/rovo89/XposedBridge\">XposedBridge</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/LSPosed/LSPosed\">LSPosed</a>\n<a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+/androidx-master-dev/annotation/annotation/\" rel=\"nofollow\">androidx.annotation</a></p>\n<h3>\n<a id=\"user-content-软件截图\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>软件截图</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/1767523953/MiuiHome/blob/main/Screenshot/pc1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://github.com/1767523953/MiuiHome/raw/main/Screenshot/pc1.jpg\" alt=\"Screenshot\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h3>\n<a id=\"user-content-license\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#license\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>License</h3>\n<p><a href=\"LICENSE\">AMTPL v1 + GPL-3.0</a></p>\n","childGitHubReadme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>MiuiHome</h1>\n<p><strong>Hook for MIUI Launcher - Xposed</strong> <a href=\"https://github.com/1767523953/MiuiHome/actions/workflows/main.yml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://github.com/1767523953/MiuiHome/actions/workflows/main.yml/badge.svg\" alt=\"Android CI\"></a></p>\n<h3>如何使用</h3>\n<p><strong>激活模块后重启一次系统桌面，再打开桌面设置，点击模块设置选项即可弹出弹窗.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>模块设置不在本应用界面!!请在MIUI桌面设置中打开Dialog来设置.</strong></p>\n<h3>前世今生</h3>\n<p><strong>原仓库：<a href=\"https://github.com/YuKongA/MiuiHome\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">YuKongA/MiuiHome</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>新仓库：<a href=\"https://github.com/1767523953/MiuiHome\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">1767523953/MiuiHome</a></strong></p>\n<h3>模块涉及内容</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>平滑动画.</li>\n<li>文件夹模糊.</li>\n<li>动画速度调节.</li>\n<li>后台模糊级别.</li>\n<li>状态栏时钟常显.</li>\n<li>后台卡片大小调节.</li>\n<li>后台卡片圆角大小调节.</li>\n<li>下载时图标的水波纹特效.</li>\n<li>后台卡片图标文字间距调节.</li>\n<li>强制为高端设备(默认启用)等.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Credit</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/ejiaogl/FuckCoolapk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">FC</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/yujincheng08/BiliRoaming/blob/master/LICENSE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">BiliRoaming</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/rovo89/XposedBridge\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">XposedBridge</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/LSPosed/LSPosed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">LSPosed</a>\n<a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+/androidx-master-dev/annotation/annotation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">androidx.annotation</a></p>\n<h3>软件截图</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/1767523953/MiuiHome/blob/main/Screenshot/pc1.jpg\" alt=\"Screenshot\"></p>\n<h3>License</h3>\n<p><a href=\"LICENSE\">AMTPL v1 + GPL-3.0</a></p>"}},"summary":"MiuiHome 自定义","scope":["com.miui.home"],"sourceUrl":"https://github.com/1767523953/MiuiHome","hide":false,"additionalAuthors":[{"type":"add","name":"QQLittleice","link":"https://github.com/1767523953"},{"type":"add","name":"YuKongA","link":"https://github.com/YuKongA"}],"updatedAt":"2021-06-14T16:36:38Z","createdAt":"2021-05-04T08:30:43Z","stargazerCount":0}